				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Okay, an update on this quest.  Yes, the rods are for the Ice Comet quest, which by the way, starts in the Everfrost Peaks, by talking to a wizard NPC.  He's right next to the zone wall, between the entrance to the plains, and the entrance to Permafrost.<BR>
<BR>
The rods are scattered throughout Norrath, and they're all NO DROP, etc.  But, they've changed the spawn time in the recent patch.  As in, I picked up the one in the water in Highhold, came back 2 minutes later, and it was there again.<BR>
<BR>
Good news for wizard's out there.
